sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Envoy as Envoy Proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>4180/TCP HTTP
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Redis as Redis (optional)<br/>6379/TCP
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Upstream as Upstream App

    rect rgb(220, 237, 200)
        Note over User,Upstream: Flow 1: OIDC Authentication (auth mode)
        User->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/start
        AuthProxy->>OIDC: 302 Redirect to authorization endpoint<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        User->>OIDC: Login with credentials<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        OIDC->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/callback?code=xxx<br/>HTTP/4180
        AuthProxy->>OIDC: POST token endpoint<br/>HTTPS/443, Client credentials + code
        OIDC-->>AuthProxy: Access token + ID token
        AuthProxy->>AuthProxy: Create session (Cookie or Redis)
        AuthProxy->>Upstream: Proxy request + injected headers<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        Upstream-->>AuthProxy: Response
        AuthProxy-->>User: Response + Set-Cookie
    end

    rect rgb(255, 242, 204)
        Note over User,Upstream: Flow 2: Kubernetes RBAC Authorization (rbac mode)
        User->>RBACProxy: Request with Bearer token<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Authenticated identity
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Allowed/Denied
        alt Allowed
            RBACProxy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>+ x-remote-user/x-remote-groups headers
            Upstream-->>RBACProxy: Response
            RBACProxy-->>User: Response
        else Denied
            RBACProxy-->>User: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    rect rgb(213, 232, 212)
        Note over User,Upstream: Flow 3: OpenShift OAuth Sign-Out
        User->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/sign_out<br/>HTTP/4180, Session cookie
        AuthProxy->>K8sAPI: DELETE OAuthAccessToken<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer access token
        K8sAPI-->>AuthProxy: Token deleted
        AuthProxy-->>User: Clear cookie + redirect
    end

    rect rgb(228, 244, 253)
        Note over User,Upstream: Flow 4: Envoy ext_authz Integration (auth mode)
        User->>Envoy: Request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3
        Envoy->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/auth<br/>HTTP/4180, Forwarded headers
        alt Authenticated (202)
            AuthProxy-->>Envoy: 202 Accepted + auth headers
            Envoy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>+ authenticated headers
            Upstream-->>Envoy: Response
            Envoy-->>User: Response
        else Not authenticated (401)
            AuthProxy-->>Envoy: 401 Unauthorized
            Envoy-->>User: Redirect to login
        end
    end
